rd interstellar\nradiation field, much larger than the rate in the Leiden photodissociation\ndatabase. In addition, we report a new $2\\,^1\\Sigma_u^+$ state that should be\ndetectable via a strong $2\\,^1\\Sigma_u^+-X\\,^1\\Sigma_g^+$ band around 116 nm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 19:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
