locities for compressive forcing. The\nnatural mixture forcing shows kinematics and gas distributions intermediate\nbetween the two extremes, the cold-phase gas occurs as both large-scale\nfilaments and small-scale misty clouds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 22:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
