ing simulated atmosphere under median seeing conditions. The\nsimulations and lab results demonstrate the HDFS as an excellent piston sensor\nfor the GMT. We find that the combination of a pyramid slope sensor with a HDFS\npiston sensor is a powerful architecture for the GMT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2022 23:15:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-09"}
