s, and the magnetic power spectrum is usually shallower in\nquiescent intervals. We propose that the temporal modulation of switchback\npatches may be related to the \"breathing\" of emerging flux that appears in\nimages as the formation of \"bubbles\" below prominences in the Hinode/SOT\nobservations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 11:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
